# duckstruct

This repository implements **duckstruct**, a programming language. The compiler, runtime pieces, and tooling are written in **Rust** (workspace crates under `crates/`).

## Type system

duckstruct uses **constraint-style type checking on function parameters** (requirements on parameters rather than only nominal types). When changing inference, diagnostics, or call typing, preserve that model and align with existing `tycheck` / parser behavior instead of assuming a conventional nominal-only system.

## Language server

The **VS Code extension and LSP server** live under **`dscode/`** (client, server, scripts). Editor behavior, protocol messages, and E2E tests belong there; keep Rust diagnostics and LSP surfaces consistent when you touch both sides.
